    "description": "斯巴达战纪是一款拥有roguelike元素的快节奏单屏幕动作游戏，在古老的竞技场内随机出现各种敌人和怪物，你能做的就是不断战斗、不断提升你的战力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/0102a47e75c419ad69965ad82060b14e.poster.avif?t=1670570732\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/0102a47e75c419ad69965ad82060b14e.webm?t=1670570732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/0102a47e75c419ad69965ad82060b14e.mp4?t=1670570732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>300名勇士离开斯巴达，站在100万波斯人和希腊的命运之间。在特莫比莱关口，经过几天的战斗，299名斯巴达人都倒下了。现在，只有你能阻止入侵者，保护你的人民！！！<br><br>你将扮演列奥尼达，斯巴达的国王，为你的人民而战。在你为阻止无尽的波斯人而战斗时，将获得令人振奋的全新蓝图和道具，每个道具都有其独特的能力，帮助你赢得胜利。<br><br>游戏特点<br>硬核、快节奏、流畅的高度随机性战斗<br>+200个改变游戏规则的道具等你探索，各种道具蓝图拿到手软<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/24750554e76115f27e7add0cfec5df27.poster.avif?t=1670570732\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/24750554e76115f27e7add0cfec5df27.webm?t=1670570732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/24750554e76115f27e7add0cfec5df27.mp4?t=1670570732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>+40种独特的敌人随机出现<br>战斗控制易上手<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/0a413fac78562aa17c2f0622d9e33064.poster.avif?t=1670570732\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/0a413fac78562aa17c2f0622d9e33064.webm?t=1670570732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/0a413fac78562aa17c2f0622d9e33064.mp4?t=1670570732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>街机风格竞技场战斗<br>多种攻击方式，与道具的结合，使每一次战斗都很独特<br>支持控制器和键盘/鼠标<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/35ad5e4a9304747b0fc9e54897e79e56.poster.avif?t=1670570732\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/35ad5e4a9304747b0fc9e54897e79e56.webm?t=1670570732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867790/extras/35ad5e4a9304747b0fc9e54897e79e56.mp4?t=1670570732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>攻击、躲避、杀戮、死亡、学习，哥们能砍你就来~<br><br>爷们要战斗！！！你能生存多少天？打败多少个波斯人呢？V我11看看实力！！！<br>玩家扣扣群：529761013<br><br>游戏支持手柄和键盘操作。键盘操作时容易与输入法按键冲突，可使用shift键进行切换调整。使用键盘操作时，可在游戏玩法设置中关闭手柄设置，防止键盘操作无响应。",
